'''Patrice Guillaume Athanase Talon''' (wuxuu dhashey 1 Meey 1958) waa siyaasi reer Benin ah ahna ganacsade madaxweynenimo ka soo noqday dalka [[Benin]] ilaa 6 Abriil 2016.

Bishii Sebtember 2021, Patrice Talon iyo Thomas Boni Yayi, xulafo siyaasadeed oo noqday cadow soke, ayaa ku kulmay Qasriga Marina ee Cotonou. Intii lagu guda jiray tête-à-tête, Thomas Boni Yayi wuxuu Patrice Talon guddoonsiiyay soo jeedinno iyo codsiyo taxane ah, gaar ahaan la xiriira sii deynta “maxaabiista siyaasadeed”.
